Interface ImcHandlerBuilder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    HandlerBuilder<ImcHandler>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultImcHandlerBuilder

    public interface ImcHandlerBuilder
extends HandlerBuilder<ImcHandler>
    Generic builder to build a message handler, handling IF-TNCCS message destined for an IMC. The builder can be used in a fluent way.
